        <div class="mx-legend-item"><div class="mx-legend-color" style="background:#7c3aed"></div> Diag. secundară</div>
        <div class="mx-legend-item"><div class="mx-legend-color" style="background:#991b1b"></div> Ambele diagonale</div>
